<p>Final touches: She completed her outfit with a pair of white sneakers and held a tote bag on her shoulder</p>

<p>Nicola is believed to be working at Pete's Byron Bay Evolve Health Labs clinic, which offers 'transformational practices' such as 'cold and conscious breath-work'.</p>

<p>Nicola, who describes herself as 'moon gazing farm girl' and 'nutritional mermaid', has raised eyebrows in recent years with her unusual beliefs about health and spirituality.</p>

<p>She also received media attention in 2017, when she went under the knife to have her 'toxic' breast implants removed. </p>

